articles.title: Grant Dalton: The stakes just raised in the America's Cup - Stuff.co.nz
articles.description: Team NZ boss on why Formula One's increasing presence in their rivals' plans emphasises the need to get the right hosting deal.
articles.content:
Grant Dalton says the growing Formula One influence on the Americas Cup emphasises Team New Zealands need to solidify their finances for the defence of the Auld Mug.
